{"tid":259550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：六四當日有驟雨及雷暴","createTime":"2017-05-27T04:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T07:56:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d10952e4c92e6f10adadfcfdc87589456c4efe9a","tid":259550,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"本港今日天氣清涼，温度介乎24度至28度，根據天文台9天天氣預報，預料未來兩日天氣仍然清涼、乾燥及部分時間有陽光，最高温29度；其後天氣轉差，周二起多雲有幾陣驟雨；周四天氣最熱，最高温31度。<br />\n<br />\n一股活躍的西南氣流會在下周末為本港帶來驟雨及雷暴，氣温下降至最高28度，周六雨勢有時頗大。至六四（周日）當天，天文台預測預測多雲、有驟雨及雷暴。"},{"pid":"e12a8bc0f848040702e312f1c1282858235c7411","tid":259550,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b61c5b15f408fab019c18c69bc4735bf115520","tid":259550,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"天文台又有任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72154b3eb258bc0d7bef87b4bad9e646907bc8a8","tid":259550,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六四夜邪壇雷電再</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c9e86ca4bd7dd6ef99333fb80d35f640a334496f","tid":259550,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六四夜邪壇雷電再</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有聲"},{"pid":"03c54c6929d2f6a32dcedfbd0129ce775e8dbfa9","tid":259550,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六四夜邪壇雷電再</span></strong></blockquo